data.description: Located in a very sought-after part of town, this 3 bedroom 2 bath home comes with an extra room that could be used as a 4th bedroom, sunroom, craft room, playroom or whatever your heart desires.  The large backyard is fenced for privacy and comes with a workshop/shed on slab.  Heat and A/C upgraded to higher efficiency units in 2011, flooring updated in 2013, roof replaced in 2014, and new gas water heater in 2020.  This neighborhood is located close to shopping, dining, and entertainment yet is so quiet and peaceful you will think you are out in the country. The best of both worlds!
